OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome cloudy areas with possible
OL,6,Fmist and patchy light rain affecting
OL,7,Fhigher ground. Turning sunnier for
OL,8,Fmost by the afternoon, especially
OL,9,Ffurther east. Feeling very warm by
OL,10,Fafternoon. Cooler over the North
OL,11,FPennines, with cloud probably
OL,12,Flingering here longest.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA fine night with mostly
OL,15,Fclear skies across the region. Some
OL,16,Fcloud likely over higher ground,
OL,17,Fespecially later in the night. Winds
OL,18,Fremaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
