OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA similar day to Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine and turning
OL,7,Fvery warm or hot by afternoon. A
OL,8,Fcooler, onshore breeze might develop
OL,9,Fnear coasts of Yorkshire later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry and sunny with hot afternoons.
OL,13,FChance of isolated thundery showers at
OL,14,Ffirst, mainly affecting hills.
OL,15,FFreshening easterly winds by Sunday.
OL,16,FTemperatures above average throughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
